Class DefaultObserver<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.reactive.DefaultRunnableObserver<T>
      • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.reactive.DefaultObserver<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the element type to observe
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer<T>, RunnableClosableObserver<T>, Closeable, AutoCloseable, Runnable

    public abstract class DefaultObserver<T>
extends DefaultRunnableObserver<T>
    A wrapper implementation for observer which is able to unregister from the Observable. Use the registerWith() and unregister() methods instead of adding this to a register() call.
    Author:
    akarnokd, 2011.01.29.
